$ Editor: ed
@ ed

ed is a line oriented → development/editors[text editor] and together with the assembler and the → Linux/shell one of the first three key elements of the Unix operating system.

ed is pronounced as *ee-dee*.

ed (as also vi) is covered by the → Linux/POSIX standard.

ed was developed by *Ken Thompson*.

sa:

  `edlin` (MS-Dos and 32-bit Versions of Windows NT) was inspired by ed and has a similar usage and syntax like ed.
